modShortDescription: This 7 Days to Die mod adds 2 new food items crafted with Super Corn as an ingredient. Added foods: Super Cornbread and Supercorn Meat Stew.
modDescription:
This 7 Days to Die mod adds 2 new [food](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-food/) items crafted with Super Corn as an ingredient.

**Added foods:**

* Super Cornbread
* Supercorn Meat Stew

**[Download](https://github.com/GopherMods/7DTDMods/raw/master/SuperCornCookedFoods.zip)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/17309-gophers-modlets-not-an-all-in-one-pack/).

**Credits:** [Gopher](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/gopher/)
